dad's old phone I left on here?

302
00:23:30,670 --> 00:23:32,170
No, I haven't.

303
00:23:32,410 --> 00:23:33,670
Really?

304
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:37,110
I clearly remember leaving it here.

305
00:24:03,300 --> 00:24:06,940
It's not here. What should I do?

306
00:24:10,710 --> 00:24:12,450
[Body Section, Themes,
Music Sync, Collaboration]

307
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:15,050
[Music Sync,
Bluetooth]

308
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:43,410
The Code of Decency

309
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:46,480
has never been brought up before.

310
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:50,650
So take this chance to do so.

311
00:24:51,790 --> 00:24:54,420
It will be filed against
junior grade one An Yi-Chan

312
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:56,320
and his mother Song Yeo-wool.

313
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:59,060
Do you have to go this far?

314
00:24:59,390 --> 00:25:02,530
What about your hotel and our foundation?

315
00:25:03,430 --> 00:25:05,100
Didn't I tell you we need Song Yeo-wool

316
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:07,870
regarding the problem with Midas Funds?

317
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:10,440
That's a separate problem.

318
00:25:11,970 --> 00:25:14,270
We can't let things stay this way
because of that.

319
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:18,150
Of course, I don't intend to push ahead
with my thoughts alone.

320
00:25:19,610 --> 00:25:21,450
Even if we need Song Yeo-wool,

321
00:25:22,220 --> 00:25:25,250
it can't be helped
if a majority of the parents want it.

322
00:25:26,650 --> 00:25:28,790
What do you mean,
a majority of the parents?

323
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:31,830
I'm going to proceed with a petition

324
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:34,160
of parents in favor of
Yi-chan leaving this school.

325
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:37,130
I'll take care of this,

326
00:25:37,730 --> 00:25:39,500
so you can sit back.

327
00:25:39,570 --> 00:25:42,900
We have to teach her what happens
if she steps out of line.

328
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:04,890
What brings you to call me?

329
00:26:10,630 --> 00:26:13,100
I'm not sure
if I have anything to say in person.

330
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:18,000
Fine. I'll meet you there.

331
00:26:39,330 --> 00:26:41,330
Why did you want to see me?

332
00:26:41,630 --> 00:26:43,500
I have something to tell you.

333
00:26:43,860 --> 00:26:46,830
And I thought a place
without many eyes would be best.

334
